<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#fab24d" style="font-family: 'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 22px; line-height: 26px; color: #ffffff;"><strong>NCS – you have hours to make up<BR> before you can graduate</strong></td>
		
